%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6
%% Source: architecture/rhoai-3.4-ea.2/kubeflow.md

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Webhook as NotebookWebhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant Controller as ODH Notebook Controller
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(openshift-ingress)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant KRBP as kube-rbac-proxy Sidecar<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant Notebook as Notebook Container<br/>8888/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 1: Notebook Creation with Auth (RHOAI 3.x)

    User->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: POST /mutate-notebook-v1<br/>Port 8443/TCP, TLS (service-ca)
    Webhook->>K8sAPI: GET ImageStreams, ConfigMaps<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Mutated Notebook<br/>(kube-rbac-proxy injected,<br/>CA certs mounted,<br/>runtime images mounted)
    K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook Created

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Controller Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceAccount,<br/>kube-rbac-proxy ConfigMap,<br/>kube-rbac-proxy Service
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>({notebook}-rbac-{ns}-auth-delegator)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ReferenceGrant<br/>(notebook-httproute-access)<br/>in user namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HTTPRoute<br/>(nb-{ns}-{notebook})<br/>in central namespace
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicies<br/>({notebook}-ctrl-np,<br/>{notebook}-kube-rbac-proxy-np)

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 2: User Accessing Notebook (Auth Mode)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBP: Forward request<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: TokenReview<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Token Valid
    KRBP->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview<br/>(get notebooks kubeflow.org)
    K8sAPI-->>KRBP: Access Granted
    KRBP->>Notebook: Forward to localhost<br/>8888/TCP HTTP plaintext<br/>X-Auth-Request-User/Groups headers
    Notebook-->>KRBP: Response
    KRBP-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Response

    Note over User,Notebook: Flow 3: User Accessing Notebook (Non-Auth Mode)

    User->>Gateway: GET /notebook/{ns}/{name}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+<br/>No Auth
    Gateway->>Notebook: Forward via ReferenceGrant<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>Cross-namespace
    Notebook-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>User: Response

    Note over Controller,K8sAPI: Flow 4: Elyra Pipeline Config Sync

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET DSPA CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET Gateway CR<br/>(for hostname)
    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET S3 credentials Secret
    Controller->>K8sAPI: CREATE/UPDATE ds-pipeline-config Secret<br/>in user namespace
